dc_title_s: LiDAR-Derived Tiled DEM for Chippewa County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents a LiDAR-derived tiled Digital Elevation Model (DEM) for Chippewa County, Wisconsin in 2020. A DEM represents the bare-Earth surface, removing all natural and built features. This dataset contains individual files available for download consisting of smaller tiled geographic areas over the extent of an entire county.
uw_supplemental_s: Detailed metadata for this data can be accessed here: https://bin.ssec.wisc.edu/pub/wisconsinview/lidar/Chippewa/Chippewa_2020_3DEP_Delivery/metadata/
